commentText: Test loads and stores with update script equivalent
codeText: public void testUpdateMapLoadStore() {_        Map<String, Object> load = new HashMap<>()__        Map<String, Object> _source = new HashMap<>()__        Map<String, Object> ctx = new HashMap<>()__        Map<String, Object> params = new HashMap<>()___        load.put("load5", "testvalue")__        _source.put("load", load)__        ctx.put("_source", _source)__        params.put("ctx", ctx)___        assertEquals("testvalue", exec("ctx._source['load'].5 = ctx._source['load'].remove('load5')", params, true))__    }
